seams.what_it_does:
For each row in the section's ev_subset it emits EXACTLY:
<<<evidence:{evidence_id}>>>
tier: {tier}
url: {source_url}
statement: {statement}
direct_quote: {direct_quote}
<<<end_evidence>>>
Five fields. Nothing else on the row is passed to the writer — not document_type, not year, not authority_score, not query_origin.
